<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Tentang CleanHouse</title>
    <!-- Fonts & Tailwind -->
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,400..900;1,400..900&family=Source+Sans+3:ital,wght@0,200..900;1,200..900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@tailwindcss/browser@4"></script>
    <style>
        body { font-family: 'Source Sans 3', sans-serif; }
        h1, h2, h3, h4, .font-display { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; letter-spacing: -0.02em; }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-[#FAFAF9] text-[#1C1917] min-h-screen flex flex-col justify-between antialiased">

    <!-- Navigation -->
    <nav class="bg-[#FAFAF9]/80 backdrop-blur-md sticky top-0 z-50 border-b border-[#D6D3D1]">
        <div class="max-w-[1200px] mx-auto px-6 py-4 flex items-center justify-between">
            <a href="/" class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#C2410C] font-display">CleanHouse.</a>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-6 text-[14px]">
                <a class="text-[#57534E] hover:text-[#1C1917] transition-colors" href="/">Katalog Jasa</a>
                <a class="font-semibold text-[#C2410C]" href="/tentang">Tentang Kami</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <!-- Main Content -->
    <main class="max-w-[1200px] mx-auto px-6 py-12 flex-1 w-full">
        <div class="text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-12">
            <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-[#1C1917] mb-3">Tentang CleanHouse</h2>
            <p class="text-[#57534E] text-[18px]">Penyedia layanan kebersihan panggilan terpercaya untuk rumah, apartemen, dan ruang usaha Anda.</p>
            <hr class="my-6 border-[#D6D3D1] opacity-50">
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 max-w-4xl mx-auto items-start">
            <!-- Left Column -->
            <div>
                <h4 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#C2410C] mb-4">Mengapa Memilih Kami?</h4>
                <p class="text-[#57534E] text-[16px] mb-4 leading-relaxed">Kami memahami bahwa waktu Anda sangat berharga. CleanHouse hadir untuk memberikan efisiensi tanpa mengorbankan kualitas kebersihan tempat tinggal Anda.</p>
                <ul class="space-y-3 text-[#57534E] text-[14px]">
                    <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                        <span class="text-[#16A34A] font-bold">✓</span>
                        <span><strong>Tim Profesional:</strong> Teknisi kebersihan terlatih, jujur, dan beridentitas jelas.</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                        <span class="text-[#16A34A] font-bold">✓</span>
                        <span><strong>Peralatan Modern:</strong> Menggunakan vacuum hydro-cleaner anti tungau dan antiseptik standar.</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                        <span class="text-[#16A34A] font-bold">✓</span>
                        <span><strong>Sistem Fleksibel:</strong> Pesan langsung via web, tim kami langsung meluncur ke lokasi sesuai jadwal.</span>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Right Column -->
            <div class="bg-[#F5F5F4] border border-[#D6D3D1] rounded-[12px] p-6 shadow-[0_4px_16px_rgba(28,25,23,0.04)]">
                <h5 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#1C1917] mb-4">Alur Pemesanan</h5>
                <ol class="list-decimal list-inside space-y-3 text-[#57534E] text-[14px]">
                    <li class="pl-1">Daftar/Login ke dalam akun Anda.</li>
                    <li class="pl-1">Pilih kategori jasa (Pembersihan harian, cuci kasur, kerak kamar mandi, dll).</li>
                    <li class="pl-1">Tentukan kuantitas sesi layanan lalu klik Pesan.</li>
                    <li class="pl-1">Simpan atau cetak struk lunas sebagai bukti sah reservasi jadwal.</li>
                </ol>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer class="bg-[#F5F5F4] text-[#78716C] py-6 border-t border-[#D6D3D1]">
        <div class="max-w-[1200px] mx-auto px-6 text-center text-[14px]">
            &copy; 2026 CleanHouse. Tangerang, Indonesia.
        </div>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>